Class ColoredPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.geom.Point2D
      • java.awt.Point
        • cellularData.ColoredPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class ColoredPoint
extends java.awt.Point
    Class ColoredPoint creates a point for the cellular graph with a given color and position (in terms of pixels) on the graph.
    Author:
    Timothy Hsu, Zach Rooney

                    double mappedX,

        Constructor that initializes the colored point for the cellular graph.
        Parameters:
        color - The color of the point
        mappedX - The x position of the point on the graph in terms of pixels
        mappedY - The y position of the point on the graph in terms of pixels
        originalX - The x position of the point on the graph in terms of the actual cellular data
